abstract: Ladbrokes, the British bookmaking chain, has added Bob Dylan's name to the list of leading contenders for the Nobel Prize in literature, which will be announced Thursday.
snippet: Ladbrokes, the British bookmaking chain, has added Bob Dylan's name to the list of leading contenders for the Nobel Prize in literature, which will be announced Thursday.
lead_paragraph: Predictions for the Nobel Prize in Literature tend to be all over the place, especially in the final hours before the winner is named. But Bob Dylan?

headline.main: Dylan Tangled Up in Nobel Prize Speculation
